<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="{{ og_description }}">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ title }} - {{ og_title_preset }}">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{ title }} - {{ og_title_preset }}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{ og_description }}">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{ public_url }}">
    <meta property="og:image" content="{{ og_image }}">
    <meta property="og:image:secure_url" content="{{ og_image_secure }}">
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="{{ og_image_width }}">
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="{{ og_image_height }}">
    <meta property="og:image:alt" content="{{ og_image_alt }}">
    <title>{{ title }} - {{ og_title_preset }}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/ppe/image/favicon.svg" sizes="any" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="mask-icon" href="/ppe/image/favicon.svg" color="yellow">
    <link rel="icon alternate" href="/ppe/image/favicon.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/ppe/image/apple-touch-icon.png" sizes="180x180">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/ppe/style.css">
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{ public_url }}">
    {% include "gtag.njk" %}
    {% include "fontplus.njk" %}
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="Breadcrumb">
      <a class="Breadcrumb__crumb" href="{{ base }}">トップ</a>
      <img class="Breadcrumb__separator" src="/ppe/image/round-triangle-right.svg" alt="" />
      <b class="Breadcrumb__crumb" aria-current="true">{{ title }}</b>
    </nav>
    {% include "header.njk" %}

    <article class="Article">
      <h1 class="Article__title">{{ title }}</h1>
      <nav>
        <ul class="ColumnList">
          <li>
            <div class="Item">
              <img class="Item__pict" src="/ppe/image/photos/mask-01_thumbnail.jpg" alt="" />
              <span class="Item__name">【縫わずに作れる！】<br>簡易マスクの作り方</span>
              <div class="Item__chip">
                <span class="Chip">手作り可</span>
                <span class="Chip">再利用可</span>
                <span class="Chip -not-recommended">医療非推奨</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="Btn" href="./01.html">性能評価と作り方を見る</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="Item">
              <img class="Item__pict" src="/ppe/image/photos/mask-02_thumbnail.jpg" alt="" />
              <span class="Item__name">高機能DIYマスク<br>「HK Mask」</span>
              <div class="Item__chip">
                <span class="Chip">手作り可</span>
                <span class="Chip">再利用可</span>
                <span class="Chip -not-recommended">医療非推奨</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="Btn" href="./02.html">性能評価と作り方を見る</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <div class="Separator"></div>

      <section class="Section" id="Reviews">
        <header class="HeadingAnchor">
          <h2>評価について</h2>
          <a href="#Reviews"><span class="VisuallyHidden">このセクションへのリンク</span></a>
        </header>

        <section class="Section__nesting" id="Assessment">
          <h3 class="Section__heading">主な評価基準</h3>
          <div class="Section__inner">
            <dl class="AssessmentList">
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>規格等</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">JIS規格の準拠に相当すると思われるか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>遮断性能</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">正面および上部等からの飛沫の進入を十分に防げるか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>運動フィット性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">小走りや振り向きなどの運動でズレないか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>快適性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">息苦しさや接触などの不快感が防止されているか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>使用耐久性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">使用中に想定される衝突や引っかきに耐えるか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>消毒耐久性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">アルコールや次亜塩素酸ナトリウムによる除染・消毒に耐えるか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>作製容易性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">作製に特別な練習を必要としないか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>省コスト性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">材料の価格や入手などのハードルは低いか</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="AssessmentList__row">
                <dt class="AssessmentList__key"><span>再利用性</span></dt>
                <dd class="AssessmentList__value">適切な除染・消毒による再度利用は可能か</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="Section__nesting">
          <h3 class="Section__heading">考案者の皆様へ</h3>
          <div class="Section__inner">
            <p>テキストが入ります</p>
            <dl class="InlineDescriptionList">
              <dt>テキストが入ります</dt>
              <dd>テキストが入ります</dd>
            </dl>
            <p>テキストが入ります</p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>
    </article>

    {% include "footer.njk" %}
  </body>
</html>
